    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年3月24日-2025年3月28日）",
    "followRuleId": "1221386336603344896",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm; background: white;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">本周共公示8条规则，生效10条规则，新增1篇规则解读。</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1221734383111770112&amp;btype=1\">《2025年第2季度大商超老带新招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30）》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在激励周期内，新入驻大商超适用品类的商家，当新商家的主营类目销售额达到3万，则推荐其入驻的老商家可获1,000元广告激励金，激励金将充值至老商家店铺对应的京准通账户，用作店铺推广。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1222749586809032704\">《2025年Q2季度京东开放平台个人/个体-手机品类POP商家激励政策》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">针对经营个人/个体店，且主营类目为手机品类的商家，其在2025年第二季度的销售额及广告消耗金额达到一定目标，即对店铺进行现金返还。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1222790318294962176&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台工业品、元器件类目激励政策》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">针对经营工业品、元器件等一级类目（运营支持服务费率&le;2%的类目不参与此次激励）的企业店新老商家，当销售金额达到指定要求，将返还相应比例的广告激励金至商家京准通账户，用作店铺推广。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1221451254555873280\">《京东开放平台个人店铺主体升级规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确个人店铺主体升级为个体户店铺<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">的相关要求和材料。</span> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1221442385255469056\">《京东开放平台经营类目商品阈值明细表》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">类目更名，珠宝首饰-合成/人造宝石调整为珠宝首饰-培育钻石/人工彩宝；②新增类目阈值及修订部分类目阈值。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1221433111884206080\">《京东开放平台水果商品品质抽检规范》</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对缺陷容忍度和处理措施进行调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【废止】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1221392945983393792\">《京东开放平台榴莲商品品质抽检规范》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">已合并至<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1087629904436137984&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台水果商品品质抽检规范》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #236fa1;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1222165137771859968\">《京喜自营工厂店商家管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容： </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">取消开放个体工商户主体类型商家入驻；②增加<span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">开放</span>1200多个三级类目。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">1</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none 0px; color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219901545294991360&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台医药类目资质标准》</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">删除二级类目&ldquo;挂号&rdquo;资质标准；调整二级类目&ldquo;在线问诊&rdquo;资质标准；处方药相关类目新增二级类目名称。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">2</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none 0px; color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211560627345166336\"><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">①物流履约因子项指标调整；②五星店铺认证规则调整。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">3</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none 0px; color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219265844798951424\"><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台车厘子/</span><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">樱桃商品管理规则</span><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">》</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">调整等级与分级标准。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">4</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none 0px; color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1220340033161138176\"><span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台赠品管理规则》</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">①细化不适合作为赠品的类目要求；②主附件、商品说明书等商品自身必备零件不得作为赠品。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">5</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; border: none